Query:
SELECT ?X WHERE
{
{
BIND(<http://www.uochb.org/chebi/1.0/terms#chebiName> AS ?X).
}
UNION
{
BIND(3 AS ?X).
}
FILTER(isIRI(?X))
}

Result:



X




http://www.uochb.org/chebi/1.0/terms#chebiName


3



Number 3 is definitely not an IRI. And the result is same even if the argument of FILTER is negative (FILTER(! isIRI(?X))).
The same situation with isURI.
